data.description: If you're looking for a stylish re-do, don't miss this one. This 3 bedroom, 1 bath home has had many updates to include new vinyl plank flooring, new front windows, total bathroom makeover, new paint & fixtures, new stainless-steel appliances and more. It offers approximately 1100 square feet of living space and the converted garage makes for a cozy 2nd living area or flex space. All appliances stay which includes the clothes washer & dryer. Contact listing broker Leah Eary at 405-370-5948 for showing information.
